	<div class="OrganizingPoolsFAQ">		
		<h2> It's easy to create a pool. </h2>
		<p> You just need to follow these steps </p>
		<ol>
			<li>Go to the main page of Quinielero</li>
			<li>Place your marker over the "Pools" tab. A sub-menu will appear</li>
			<li>Click on the "Organize Pools" tab in the sub-menu. You will be redirected to the pool creation page</li>
			<li>Give a name to your pool. It can be anything, but make sure to use a nice and atractive name, so people will join your pool</li>
			<li>Select a league for your pool. There are several options. Choose the one that fits you the most</li>
			<li>Set a maximum and minimum number of participants. Keep in mind that your pool wont be able to start if it doesnt have enough participants to satisfy the minimum number of participants.</li>
			<li>Set a price for your pool!. All members must pay this fee in order to enter to the pool</li>
			<li>Choose a date for your pool to start.</li>
			<li>Select the option for inviting people yo your pool right now, or do iot later manually</li>
			<li>Check all your pool's settings one more time!</li>
			<li>Click on the submit button</li>
			<li>Congratulations! You've just created a pool! Have fun</li>			
		</ol>			
